snippet.title: Disney Heroes: Battle Mode Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Join the battle in this action-packed RPG starring Disney and Pixar heroes from The Incredibles, Wreck-It Ralph, Toy Story, and more!

Pre-Register to be one of the first to receive a free hero at launch!
http://www.disneyheroesgame.com

Coming soon on the Apple App Store and Google Play Store!
